.TH PULSE-VISUALIZER 1 "@CMAKE_PROJECT_VERSION@" "Pulse Visualizer"

.SH NAME
pulse-visualizer \- Real-time audio visualizer for PulseAudio

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B Pulse
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
Pulse Visualizer is a real-time audio visualizer that displays audio from PulseAudio
in various visual formats including bars, circles, and other effects.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit

.SH CONFIGURATION
The application reads its configuration from \fI~/.config/pulse-visualizer/config.json\fR.
If this file doesn't exist, it will be created from a template on first run.

.SH THEMES
Themes are stored in \fI~/.config/pulse-visualizer/themes/\fR and can be selected
through the configuration file.

.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/pulse-visualizer/config.json
Configuration file
.TP
.I ~/.config/pulse-visualizer/themes/
Theme files directory

.SH AUTHOR
Written for the Pulse Visualizer project.

